      <reaction compartment="compartment_7660" fast="false" id="reaction_156673" metaid="metaid_18" name="Regulation of KIF23 (MKLP1) by phosphorylation" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The polo-like kinase PLK1 phosphorylates KIF23 (also known as MKLP1 i.e. mitotic kinesin-like protein 1) on serine residues S911 and S912.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
