      <reaction compartment="compartment_7660" fast="false" id="reaction_156723" metaid="metaid_20" name="Regulation of KIF20A (MKL2) by phosphorylation" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The polo-like kinase PLK1 phosphorylates KIF20A (also known as MKLP2 i.e. mitotic kinesin-like protein 2) on serine residue S528.</p>
